name: Jasgh Phrasm - Inky stylized drawings
description:
This is a bit of an odd model I threw together using a lot of SamDoesArt and Inkpunk to create a fairly unique and colorful style.

This can do landscapes, people, animals, and really anything in both a colorful inkpunk and realistic style.
